

MARINIG

   root word: dinig

   Walang akong marinig.
   I can’t hear anything.

   Wala akong narinig.
   I didn’t hear anything.

   Gusto kong marinig ang boses mo.
   I want to hear your voice.

   Dinggin mo ang aking pakiusap.
   Hear my request. / Listen to my plea.

   Pakinggan mo ako.
   Listen to me.
